      <title>泰国能源亿万富翁加大数据中心建设力度，抢占人工智能热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thai-energy-billionaire-steps-up-data-center-push-to-tap-ai-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国第二大富豪、能源亿万富翁萨拉特·拉塔纳瓦迪 (Sarath Ratanavadi) 正在加速进军数据中心领域，以挖掘云计算和人工智能需求不断增长所推动的蓬勃发展的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thai-energy-billionaire-steps-up-data-center-push-to-tap-ai-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:05:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
